        "responses": {
          "values": [
            {
              "content": "=You are a strict data extractor.\nExtract factual information from the text provided below and convert it into Question-Answer pairs optimized for a vector database.\n\nSTRICT RULES:\n1. Generate 1 to 5 Q/A pairs. If there is not enough information, generate fewer.\n2. ONLY use the provided text. Do not invent, guess, or infer anything.\n3. STANDALONE CONTEXT: Every generated question MUST be highly specific and self-contained (e.g., instead of \"What is the triangle?\", use \"What are the three pillars of the credibility triangle for freelancers?\").\n4. LANGUAGE RULE: All generated questions and answers MUST be exclusively in Standard Arabic (Fusha), regardless of the input language.\n5. FORMAT: You must strictly output a valid JSON object containing a single key \"qna\" with an array of objects. Do NOT wrap the JSON in markdown formatting or code blocks. Output ONLY raw JSON.\n\nExpected JSON format:\n{\n  \"qna\": [\n    { \"question\": \"السؤال الدقيق هنا...\", \"answer\": \"الجواب هنا...\" }\n  ]\n}\n\nTEXT TO ANALYZE:\n###\n{{ $json.chunk }}\n###"
            }
          ]
        },
        "simplify": false,
        "builtInTools": {},
        "options": {
